															},
															"Children": [
																{
																	"Type": "NodeText",
																	"Data": "每个chassis上的ovn-controller控制器进程接收更新后的南向数据库和更新后的"
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeCodeSpan",
																	"Data": "code",
																	"Children": [
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanOpenMarker"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanContent",
																			"Data": "nb_cfg"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanCloseMarker"
																		}
																	]
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeText",
																	"Data": "。\n该过程也会更新chassis的Open vSwitch实例上安装的物理流（physical flows）。\n当它从Open vSwitch收到物理流已更新的确认信息时，就会在南向数据库中更新自己的Chassis记录中的nb_cfg。"
																}
															]
														}
													]
												}
											]
										}
									]
								},
								{
									"ID": "20221129003002-x55h2ev",
									"Type": "NodeListItem",
									"ListData": {
										"BulletChar": 42,
										"Marker": "Kg=="
									},
									"Properties": {
										"id": "20221129003002-x55h2ev"
									},
									"Children": [
										{
											"ID": "20221129003002-6zussga",
											"Type": "NodeList",
											"ListData": {
												"Typ": 1
											},
											"Properties": {
												"id": "20221129003002-6zussga"
											},
											"Children": [
												{
													"ID": "20221129003002-homw2zq",
													"Type": "NodeListItem",
													"ListData": {
														"Typ": 1,
														"Delimiter": 46,
														"Marker": "NS4=",
														"Num": 5
													},
													"Properties": {
														"id": "20221129003002-homw2zq"
													},
													"Children": [
														{
															"ID": "20221129003002-63bcyax",
															"Type": "NodeParagraph",
															"Properties": {
																"id": "20221129003002-63bcyax"
															},
															"Children": [
																{
																	"Type": "NodeText",
																	"Data": "ovn-northd 监视所有南向数据库中Chassis记录的nb_cfg列。\n它跟踪所有记录中的最小值，并将其复制到北向"
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeCodeSpan",
																	"Data": "code",
																	"Children": [
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanOpenMarker"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanContent",
																			"Data": "NB_Global"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanCloseMarker"
																		}
																	]
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeText",
																	"Data": "表的"
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeCodeSpan",
																	"Data": "code",
																	"Children": [
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanOpenMarker"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanContent",
																			"Data": "hv_cfg"
																		},
																		{
																			"Type": "NodeCodeSpanCloseMarker"
																		}
																	]
																},
																{
																	"Type": "NodeText",
																	"Data": "列中。\n（这样一来，CMS或另一个观察者就可以确定什么时候所有hypervisor都赶上了北向配置。）"
																}
